Class SequentialProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudbus.foggatewaylib.core.Provider<T,S>
      • org.cloudbus.foggatewaylib.core.AndroidProvider<T,S>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the input data

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Base64Provider, BitmapProvider, DummyProvider, FogBusProvider, LocalProvider

    public abstract class SequentialProvider<T extends Data,S extends Data>
extends AsyncProvider<T,S>
    AsyncProvider that uses a dedicated Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor() for scheduling its tasks. As a result its tasks will be executed one after the other.
    Author:
    Riccardo Mancini
    See Also:
    Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor(), ThreadPoolProvider
